CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 11, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "Yum, Yum!... Children had fun too.  Lyda Jo Boswell feeds little Jimmie Rickmond.  Bill Gamble, Barbara Ann Boswell, Herman Scott  and David Washington are also engaged in consuming ice cream. - All Photos By Harris."
TitMainTitle: Children eating ice cream, including Lyda Jo Boswell feeding Jimmy Richmond or Rickmond in front, and Billy Gamble, Barbara Ann Boswell, Herman Scott, and David B. Washington, at FROGS picnic, South Park
